@DATABASE "Cliff Hanger"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - C - Cliff Hanger"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - C
                   ====================================

                               Cliff Hanger
                               ============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(26515,100)"}               26515,x (x= 1-100)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 100).
@endnode
